    ["QUI includes many small quality-of-life improvements: auto-repair, auto-sell junk, improved tooltips, chat enhancements, a crosshair overlay, skyriding helpers, and more."] = "QUI includes many small quality-of-life improvements: auto-repair, auto-sell junk, improved tooltips, chat enhancements, a crosshair overlay, skyriding helpers, and more.",
