    ["What happens to bars when the tracked buff is not active: always show, fade to the alpha below, or hide entirely."] = "What happens to bars when the tracked buff is not active: always show, fade to the alpha below, or hide entirely.",
    ["What is QUI Layout Mode?"] = "What is QUI Layout Mode?",
    ["What is QUI?"] = "What is QUI?",
    ["What is the Cooldown Manager (CDM)?"] = "What is the Cooldown Manager (CDM)?",
    ["What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt."] = "What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt.",
    ["What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt. Applies everywhere the Alts datatext is shown, including datatext panels."] = "What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt. Applies everywhere the Alts datatext is shown, including datatext panels.",
    ["What the alert is anchored to: the screen, the CDM Essential bar, or your focus unit frame."] = "What the alert is anchored to: the screen, the CDM Essential bar, or your focus unit frame.",
    ["What this binding does: cast a spell or macro, change target/focus/assist, open the unit menu, or send a ping. Spell and Macro reveal an input below for the spell name or macro body."] = "What this binding does: cast a spell or macro, change target/focus/assist, open the unit menu, or send a ping. Spell and Macro reveal an input below for the spell name or macro body.",
    ["What's New"] = "What's New",
    ["When Blizzard would open a whisper in a new window (right-click popout, or the 'open whispers in a new window' setting), open a QUI conversation tab instead."] = "When Blizzard would open a whisper in a new window (right-click popout, or the 'open whispers in a new window' setting), open a QUI conversation tab instead.",
    ["When ON (default), Healing Done / HPS sum each source's healing AND absorb shields. Turn off for pure HealingDone (matching Blizzard's stock meter)."] = "When ON (default), Healing Done / HPS sum each source's healing AND absorb shields. Turn off for pure HealingDone (matching Blizzard's stock meter).",
    ["When ON (default), clear all damage-meter sessions when a Mythic+ key starts so Overall begins at zero for that run."] = "When ON (default), clear all damage-meter sessions when a Mythic+ key starts so Overall begins at zero for that run.",
    ["When ON (default), hide realm names: show \"Name\" instead of \"Name-Realm\" for cross-realm players on rows, tooltips, and the breakdown popup."] = "When ON (default), hide realm names: show \"Name\" instead of \"Name-Realm\" for cross-realm players on rows, tooltips, and the breakdown popup.",
    ["When ON (default), rows show the other metric in parentheses — e.g. DPS mode shows 1.5M (42.3M). Turn off to show only the primary value."] = "When ON (default), rows show the other metric in parentheses — e.g. DPS mode shows 1.5M (42.3M). Turn off to show only the primary value.",
    ["When ON, windows showing Overall switch to Current when a key starts, then Current switches back to Overall when the key completes."] = "When ON, windows showing Overall switch to Current when a key starts, then Current switches back to Overall when the key completes.",
    ["When Swap to Primary Position is active, also hide the primary power bar so both resources aren't shown together."] = "When Swap to Primary Position is active, also hide the primary power bar so both resources aren't shown together.",
    ["When an NPC gossip has a single option, pick it automatically so you skip the popup."] = "When an NPC gossip has a single option, pick it automatically so you skip the popup.",
    ["When bars appear: always, only while the tracked buff/debuff is active, or only while in combat."] = "When bars appear: always, only while the tracked buff/debuff is active, or only while in combat.",
    ["When class color is off, use QUI accent color. Otherwise the custom Bar Color below is used."] = "When class color is off, use QUI accent color. Otherwise the custom Bar Color below is used.",
    ["When enabled, the macro selections below are stored per-character instead of being shared by every character on this AceDB profile. The toggle itself is always per-character. Turning it on copies your current profile selections as a starting point."] = "When enabled, the macro selections below are stored per-character instead of being shared by every character on this AceDB profile. The toggle itself is always per-character. Turning it on copies your current profile selections as a starting point.",
    ["When hovering a dead unit, any spell binding is temporarily replaced by your class's resurrection spell if you know one. Restores the original spell when the unit is alive."] = "When hovering a dead unit, any spell binding is temporarily replaced by your class's resurrection spell if you know one. Restores the original spell when the unit is alive.",
    ["When icons appear: always visible, only while the spell is active/on cooldown, or only while in combat."] = "When icons appear: always visible, only while the spell is active/on cooldown, or only while in combat.",
    ["When icons appear: always, only when the buff is active, or only while in combat."] = "When icons appear: always, only when the buff is active, or only while in combat.",
    ["When on, %s messages use the days slider on the right instead of the default retention. When off, the default applies."] = "When on, %s messages use the days slider on the right instead of the default retention. When off, the default applies.",
    ["When on, dragging only works while holding the move modifier. When off, any plain left-click drag repositions supported windows."] = "When on, dragging only works while holding the move modifier. When off, any plain left-click drag repositions supported windows.",
    ["When recalling a message with Up/Down, also restore its original chat type (Say, Yell, Whisper target, channel) so pressing Enter sends to the same destination."] = "When recalling a message with Up/Down, also restore its original chat type (Say, Yell, Whisper target, channel) so pressing Enter sends to the same destination.",
    ["When remaining duration drops below this, the bar switches to the Low-Time Color."] = "When remaining duration drops below this, the bar switches to the Low-Time Color.",
    ["When the anchor target is hidden but this frame stays visible, keep it at its last screen position instead of snapping toward the hidden anchor."] = "When the anchor target is hidden but this frame stays visible, keep it at its last screen position instead of snapping toward the hidden anchor.",
    ["When the native meter is visible. Always = shown at all times; In Combat = only during combat; Hidden = meter exists but is invisible."] = "When the native meter is visible. Always = shown at all times; In Combat = only during combat; Hidden = meter exists but is invisible.",
    ["When the primary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.)."] = "When the primary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.).",
    ["When the secondary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.)."] = "When the secondary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.).",
    ["When the secondary resource is dominant for your spec, swap it into the primary bar's position for that spec."] = "When the secondary resource is dominant for your spec, swap it into the primary bar's position for that spec.",
    ["When the skyriding bar is shown: always on, only while flying, or auto-fade out shortly after you land."] = "When the skyriding bar is shown: always on, only while flying, or auto-fade out shortly after you land.",
    ["When to show the icon: always visible, only in combat, or only when you have a hostile target."] = "When to show the icon: always visible, only in combat, or only when you have a hostile target.",
    ["When to show tooltips for items in your bags and equipment. Modifier options only show the tooltip while the key is held."] = "When to show tooltips for items in your bags and equipment. Modifier options only show the tooltip while the key is held.",
